summary: Comprehensive testing of Admin Logs feature and related UI enhancements completed. All backend APIs and frontend features working correctly. Admin logs page displays valid cookies with full details, navbar correctly shows/hides admin links based on user role, dashboard footer note and results sections are properly implemented.

GET /api/admin/logs returns 401 for unauthenticated users
GET /api/admin/logs returns 403 for non-admin users
DELETE /api/admin/logs/{log_id} returns 404 for non-existent log
DELETE /api/admin/logs clears all logs successfully
POST /api/check with expired cookies does NOT create log entry
Admin user login returns is_master=true
Navbar shows 'Logs' link only for admin users (is_master=true)
Navbar shows 'Keys' link only for admin users
Non-admin users do NOT see Keys or Logs links in navbar
Dashboard footer shows 'Created by Schiro. Not for Sale.'
Dashboard results separated into Valid/Expired/Invalid sections
EXPIRED COOKIES section shows with red header
Admin logs page accessible at /admin/logs with proper UI
Admin logs page shows logged cookies with email, plan, country, member_since, checked_by
Admin logs page shows NFToken with copy button
Admin logs page has 'CLEAR ALL' button
Admin logs page has expandable 'VIEW COOKIES' section
Non-admin users redirected away from /admin/logs
Textarea clears after checking cookies
